descr: "A financial tool for tracking value accrued for a particular purpose.  In the healthcare field, used to track charges for a patient, cost centers, etc."

fields.name: identifier
fields.descr: "Unique identifier used to reference the account.  May or may not be intended for human use (e.g. credit card number)."

fields.name: status
fields.descr: "Indicates whether the account is presently used/usable or not."

fields.name: name
fields.descr: "Name used for the account when displaying it to humans in reports, etc."

fields.name: period
fields.descr: "Identifies the period of time the account applies to; e.g. accounts created per fiscal year, quarter, etc."

fields.name: active
fields.descr: "Indicates the period of time over which the account is allowed to have transactions posted to it.\nThis period may be different to the coveragePeriod which is the duration of time that services may occur."

fields.name: description
fields.descr: "Provides additional information about what the account tracks and how it is used."
